comments.body: The bad thing you did was why did you place the miner on the window if you know that it was very cold outside?There are lots of issues that can happen like what happens to your miner shorted/burnt fan it is due to moisture or the plug and terminal have full of rust very cold room can make plugs and terminal rusty.Possibly after you replace the fan it works but you just didn't notice testing it a few times until the miner is hot will make the miner work again.And take note better check the kernel logs again you should see how it solves your problem.Last important note edit your thread and put all kernel logs into the insert code tag it's a # button you can find this button while editing your post.
